		<updated>1912-01-01T01:25:00+00:00</updated>
		<id>https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/14-the-last-redoubt</id>
		<author>
			<name>William Hope Hodgson</name>
			<email>coady.k@protonmail.com</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By William Hope Hodgson&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/14-the-last-redoubt&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/fabian-redoubt-grey-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;An armed man outside a tall pyramid in green mist.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;&quot;It was not as if I &lt;i&gt;dreamed;&lt;/i&gt; but, as it were, that I &lt;i&gt;waked&lt;/i&gt; there into the dark, in the future of this world. And the sun had died...&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;feed-readmore&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/14-the-last-redoubt&quot;&gt;Read More ...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By William Hope Hodgson&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/14-the-last-redoubt&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/fabian-redoubt-grey-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;An armed man outside a tall pyramid in green mist.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;&quot;It was not as if I &lt;i&gt;dreamed;&lt;/i&gt; but, as it were, that I &lt;i&gt;waked&lt;/i&gt; there into the dark, in the future of this world. And the sun had died...&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
