		<title>The Seeker</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/59-the-seeker"/>
		<published>2003-07-12T13:08:45+00:00</published>
		<updated>2003-07-12T13:08:45+00:00</updated>
		<id>https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/59-the-seeker</id>
		<author>
			<name>Carole Carmen</name>
			<email>coady.k@protonmail.com</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/about/authors-and-artists/154-carole-carmen&quot;&gt;Carole Carmen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/59-the-seeker&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/fabian-past-house-of-silence-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A man and a cloaked woman confront a high, ominous, gabled Gothic house, beside a road in darkness.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;In recent years, a tall figure in shattered grey armour has been seen wandering the Road Where The Silent Ones Walk. It is not known if this is a True Human — scholars continue to debate. But he has become known to all as The Seeker.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;feed-readmore&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/59-the-seeker&quot;&gt;Read More ...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/about/authors-and-artists/154-carole-carmen&quot;&gt;Carole Carmen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/59-the-seeker&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/fabian-past-house-of-silence-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A man and a cloaked woman confront a high, ominous, gabled Gothic house, beside a road in darkness.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;In recent years, a tall figure in shattered grey armour has been seen wandering the Road Where The Silent Ones Walk. It is not known if this is a True Human — scholars continue to debate. But he has become known to all as The Seeker.&lt;/p&gt;
